data.description: Looking for country living while still being close to all the essentials? Welcome home to your adorable farmhouse on almost 3 ACRES!! This fully updated cape cod has so much space and character. On the main floor you will find 2 bedrooms and a bonus room that has been used as a MASSIVE master bedroom making this a 5 bedroom home, as well as a designated office, 2 full bathrooms, and first floor laundry! Upstairs- two more spacious bedrooms with plenty of closet space. With a living room AND family room, you have the perfect layout to gather with friends and family. Stepping outside, Enjoy your morning coffee on your covered front porch or a relaxing glass of wine in your 4 seasons room. Although this property is in Elyria, it falls in the Keystone School district which is rated in the top 20% of districts in Lorain county! Sitting on almost 3 acres of wooded land, you have picturesque views and so much space to enjoy. The garage/outbuilding is insulated and equipped with a 220V electric line. It has a paved carport overhang as well as indoor space for 2 vehicles plus any other equipment you may need. With 3 rooms in the back and a rear facing garage door, you have endless opportunities for a workshop or animal pen. The yard is also equipped with an invisible fence to keep your pets contained! Roof replaced 2019, septic tank replaced 2020, furnace/ac 2016. Don't wait to schedule your personal showing today and make this beauty yours!
